Package org.hl7.cdsinputspecification.r2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CDSInputSpecification
    The parent class containing the data required by a specific CDS use case.
    ClinicalStatementInputSpecification
    Specifies the clinical statements required regarding the evaluated person of interest.
    CodedAttributeRequirement
    A requirement for a coded attribute of a clinical statement.
    EvaluatedPersonInputSpecification
    Specifies the data required for an evaluated person.
    ObjectFactory
    This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the org.hl7.cdsinputspecification.r2 package.
    PatientInputSpecification
    The data required for the patient.
    RelatedEntityInputSpecification
    Specifies the data required regarding entities related to the evaluated person of interest.
    RelatedEvaluatedPersonInputSpecification
    The data required for evaluated persons related to the patient.
    TimeAttributeRequirement
    A requirement for a time attribute of a clinical statement.
